version_description:
- Selectable Time Intervals Between Multi-Shot Added 
- Settings Saved (Thanks to your requests) 
- New Icon 
- Added iPhone 5 screen layout 

Follow us @MadCalfApps on Twitter & Facebook to get news, updates, and a FREE APP every Thursday! 

Thanks & Enjoy, 
Nick

- New Screenshots
- New and Improved User Interface 
- Gallery Navigation Improvements (to resize photos in iOS 7, edit in the native photo app) 

If you like Photo Timer+, please take the time to give us a nice review: it really helps.

Thanks & Enjoy, 
Nick

Thanks!
Nick
